  characterName: Milk President Keyes
  frames:
  - characterDialogue: Good to see you Master Chef.
    responses:
    - President Keyes
  - characterDialogue: Things aren't going well. Cowtana did her best, but we never
      really had a chance.
    responses:
    - ...
  - characterDialogue: A Cowvenant fleet is bearing down on us. I need you to take
      Cowtana down to that mysterious Halo-shaped structure below us [legally distinct].
    responses:
    - ...
  - characterDialogue: She'll fill you in on the details, but make it quick! We've
      got cow boarding parties bearing down on us!
    responses:
    - ...
  - characterDialogue: Take my pistol, son. I don't keep it loaded, so you'll have
      to find ammo on the way.
    responses:
    - The best gun in the game in the first mission???
